{"tid":1985091,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[教育界]請各位fresh grad留意唔好加入紅底組織","createTime":"2020-04-23T02:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T17:30:42.000Z","uid":220798,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc11465bbaa512d6144bb8c43019865d96e367ca","tid":1985091,"uid":220798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T02:16:07.000Z","msg":"懶人包：中共知道教育界多黃，唯有暗地裏用啲拿喳手段統戰，想用搵教席支援由新人入手染紅教育界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家都留意多啲，入會入link前睇清楚啲組織咩料，唔好比人呃！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又到教育界搵工季<br />\n今年咁嘅環境個個人心惶惶<br />\n擔心搵唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咦收到院校宣傳出面工會可以幫手準備搵工喎，望下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QSfNrN2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQSfNrN2.jpg&h=3bafe7bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喂屌正喎，又教interview又有前線教師指導<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個咁好人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咦教聯？紅底個個？望下咩料先<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AbOjhUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbOjhUy.jpg&h=5ec1e171&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n紅到出面喎ching，都係算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉咁上fb 啲教師secret page望下啦，睇下有冇料攞到<br />\n咦，呢條comment個個post都見到嘅？咩嚟？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nrnoKzF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnrnoKzF.jpg&h=263a0420&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好有心！即刻入link先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吖都係唔好，起下底睇下咩料先，費事好似教聯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPABj7R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPABj7R.jpg&h=d967ea73&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvLYysU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvLYysU.jpg&h=075691ed&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n喂好似正正常常咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再望下宗旨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qWeZhUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqWeZhUA.jpg&h=6305cbb4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n嗯大致都正常啦，係有個咩國情教育怪怪哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋加入即係要認同佢同母會宗旨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然入會有呢句都好似正常，但個乜新一代協會咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇埋佢官網先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f71MHmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff71MHmg.jpg&h=33943db6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一入去就見到林鄭個八婆嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要大大個國情教育擺頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一於入去睇下講咩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TqyjhUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqyjhUD.jpg&h=50c1ac2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x5DSCUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx5DSCUE.jpg&h=68d2042e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n仆街紅撚到咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶人認識祖國？祖你老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n呢個世界冇咁大隻蛤乸隨街跳<br />\n啲組織冇端端點解要花咁多心力時間去幫你班fresh grad搵工？<br />\n你估真係咁有心，幫新人入行搶佢哋飯碗？<br />\n比少少恩惠你，你就以為佢哋好好？<br />\n收中共錢吸納新人，然後攞你哋資料，攞埋個會員人數話好多老師支持佢哋啲紅底主張咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「入個whatsapp group睇下啫，唔代表咩喎」<br />\n「入去攞住着數先，用佢資源，有咩事咪走囉」<br />\n個人資料同人數攞哂啦，使鬼理你真係真心支持？你食佢個少少資源係咪會蝕死佢哋啊？佢哋後面大大條水喉泵水啦！<br />\n明白大家搵工辛苦，有人幫手講下經驗比下意見係好好多，但係咪要出賣你嘅信念，入埋哂啲紅底組織？<br />\n咁同加入民建聯有咩分別？<br />\n冇呢啲支援，一樣可以搵到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n改cv﹑改求職信可以搵院校相關部門幫手（點都有啲咩career部門﹑語文中心之類嘅嘢啩？）<br />\n面試資訊上網搵大把，會問嘅問題年年大同小異，google下﹑上教師心聲睇下都知得七七八八<br />\n希望大家唔好比啲紅底組織嘅小恩小惠收賣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝大家搵工順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後推介個新工會：教學同行陣線<br />\n教協係廢，但好多有心人都一齊努力緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油！"},{"pid":"231310f77289259297da4fc5c1d2afd97c5c8718","tid":1985091,"uid":220798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到好多fresh grad都冇為意就入咗會，希望大家睇完個post小心啲，或者share比朋友同學睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b644437167fca79b9759e6f6edad26b4cde7e112","tid":1985091,"uid":47710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T02:36:28.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51efe30ceb466c63ef0c0b8ec5a62903c62b5d7","tid":1985091,"uid":83942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64c8a43d12b841768b9d24b0aaa1a3d34b028584","tid":1985091,"uid":220798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T02:49:28.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"397fbb35b8f92